{
  "chapter": 27,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十七回\"杀搏\"。小方在拉萨与一个饲养飞鸟的孩子交谈，孩子透露其父被独孤痴一剑斩杀十三只飞鸟后当晚便死于独孤痴剑下，孩子虽知独孤痴将来会用鸟试剑却仍收容了他，只为成为那样的剑客。小方前往鹰记商号借钱时，被藏族高僧普松引至荒郊，普松以密宗大手印血掌突袭小方，声称要小方死。小方无剑在身，退至枯树下生死关头顿悟心剑之理——以枯枝为剑、以心驭剑，一击洞穿普松血掌并刺入其眼。普松重伤之际喃喃呼唤波娃之名，道出波娃要他带小方去见她，他宁死不肯，只为独占波娃之情。普松临终将护身金佛托付小方，求其持佛去布达拉宫求见噶伦喇嘛。小方随后在布达拉宫阴暗禅房中见到噶伦喇嘛，噶伦表示明白普松之痛唯死可解。本章揭示了小方在无剑困境中领悟心剑的武学突破，以及普松为情殉命的悲剧。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孩子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "它是我的朋友。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_hai_zi",
      "text": "我知道。我知道它们都是你的朋友。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孩子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "可是我对不起它们。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_hai_zi",
      "text": "为什么！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孩子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "因为我知道迟早总有一天，它们会全都死在独孤痴的剑下。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孩子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "只要等到他的手可以握剑时，就一定会用它们来试剑的。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_hai_zi",
      "text": "你怎么知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孩子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "有一次他曾经一剑斩杀了十三只飞鸟，那天晚上，他就死在独孤痴剑下。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 27
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_hai_zi",
      "text": "它们虽然是你的朋友，可是你说不定也有一天会用它来试剑的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孩子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "不错，说不定，我也会用它们来试剑的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_hai_zi",
      "text": "你亲眼看见他杀了你父亲，明知他要杀你的朋友，却还是收容了他。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孩子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "因为我也想做他们那样的剑客。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_hai_zi",
      "text": "总有一天，你一定也会成为他们那样的剑客。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孩子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "朱云",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "有人在等你，已经等了很久。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhu_yun",
      "text": "什么人？在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "朱云",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "就在这里！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_pu_song",
      "text": "我姓方，我就是小方。你是不是来找我的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pu_song",
      "speaker_name": "普松",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_pu_song",
      "text": "可是我不认得你。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pu_song",
      "speaker_name": "普松",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我也不认得你。你也不认得我。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_pu_song",
      "text": "你来找我干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pu_song",
      "speaker_name": "普松",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你要知道我为什么找你，你就跟我来！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pu_song",
      "speaker_name": "普松",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我叫普松。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pu_song",
      "speaker_name": "普松",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我来找你。因为我要你死！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_pu_song",
      "text": "我知道你要我死，刚才我差一点就死在你手里。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pu_song",
      "speaker_name": "普松",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你是剑客，你应该明白。剑客要杀人，只要能杀死那个人就好，随便用什么手段都没有关系。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pu_song",
      "speaker_name": "普松",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你是剑客，随时都可以杀人，随时都可以被人杀，你杀了人，你不会怪你自己，你被人杀，也不应该怪别人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_pu_song",
      "text": "你怎么知道我是剑客？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pu_song",
      "speaker_name": "普松",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我不认得你，但是我听人说过你，你是中土有名的剑客。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pu_song",
      "speaker_name": "普松",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你是剑客，剑客的剑，就是人的手，每个人的手都应该长在手上；每个剑客的剑都应该在身上，可是你没有。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pu_song",
      "speaker_name": "普松",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你练的是剑，你杀人用剑。我不练剑，我杀人不用剑，我用手就能杀人。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pu_song",
      "speaker_name": "普松",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我还有手，你却没有剑了，所以我不会死，我要你死！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pu_song",
      "speaker_name": "普松",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "波娃……波娃……",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_pu_song",
      "text": "是不是波娃要你来杀我的？是不是？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pu_song",
      "speaker_name": "普松",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "她要我带你去见她，我不能带你去见她，我宁可死。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pu_song",
      "speaker_name": "普松",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我不能要你死，我自己死，等我死了，你才能去见她。我活着时，谁也不能把她抢走！",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pu_song",
      "speaker_name": "普松",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我已将死，你可以去了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pu_song",
      "speaker_name": "普松",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你到布达拉宫去，带着我的护身佛去，去求见噶伦喇嘛，就说我……我已经解脱了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "speaker_name": "噶伦喇嘛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我明白你的意思。我也知道普松的痛苦只有死才能解脱。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 379
    }
  ],
